Congenital heart diseases and cardiovascular abnormalities in 22q11.2 deletion 
syndrome: From well-established knowledge to new frontiers.

Unolt M(1), Versacci P(1), Anaclerio S(1), Lambiase C(1), Calcagni G(2), Trezzi 
M(2), Carotti A(2), Crowley TB(3), Zackai EH(3), Goldmuntz E(4), Gaynor JW(4), 
