Purple head broccoli (Brassica oleracea L. var. italica Plenck), a functional 
food crop for antioxidant and anticancer potential.

Chaudhary A(1)(2), Choudhary S(3), Sharma U(2), Vig AP(1), Singh B(2), Arora 
S(1).

Author information:
(1)1Department of Botanical and Environmental Sciences, Guru Nanak Dev 
University, Amritsar, Punjab 143005 India.
(2)2Present Address: Natural Product Chemistry and Process Development Division, 
